-news/2024-03-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-three-soldiers-killed-in-khan-yunis-blast-on-friday-14-wounded-five-severely/0000018e-00bd-d4e1-abce-09bdd66e0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管内塔尼亚胡反对，甘茨仍将前往华盛顿，与副总统哈里斯会面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article/netanyahu-tries-to-thwart-gantzs-washington-trip-vp-harris-to-meet-war-cabinet-member/0000018e-0094-dd6a-a18f-eadd64490000</link><description>一位与内塔尼亚胡关系密切的消息人士称，总理昨晚向甘茨明确表示，他不赞成他前往华盛顿。然而，与战时内阁成员关系密切的消息人士否认两人之间因这次会面而存在任何紧张关系</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 19:39:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article/netanyahu-tries-to-thwart-gantzs-washington-trip-vp-harris-to-meet-war-cabinet-member/0000018e-0094-dd6a-a18f-eadd64490000</guid></item><item><title>美国称以色列接受加沙协议大纲，实施取决于哈马斯同意释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article/u-s-says-israel-accepts-gaza-deal-outline-hinges-on-hamas-agreeing-to-hostage-release/0000018e-0031-d4e1-abce-0935e7d40000</link><description>这位官员表示，以色列人“或多或少”接受了这项协议。他说：“如果哈马斯释放病人、伤员、老人和妇女人质，事情可能从今天开始——这已经摆在桌面上了。”</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 18:32:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article/u-s-says-israel-accepts-gaza-deal-outline-hinges-on-hamas-agreeing-to-hostage-release/0000018e-0031-d4e1-abce-0935e7d40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数千人抗议政府；七人在特拉维夫被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article/.premium/thousands-rally-across-israel-against-netanyahu-government-demand-early-elections/0000018e-0041-d4e1-abce-096527bf0000</link><description>在特拉维夫，警察和抗议者之间爆发冲突，当示威者开始在主干道上游行时，警方认为集会非法；海法、贝尔谢巴以及凯撒利亚内塔尼亚胡私人住宅附近也发生了示威活动</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 18:15:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article/.premium/thousands-rally-across-israel-against-netanyahu-government-demand-early-elections/0000018e-0041-d4e1-abce-096527bf0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 148 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-148/0000018e-0053-da4e-adbf-82fb64910000</link><description>美国首次向加沙空投援助 ■ 拜登表示，他“相信以色列将调查”援助分发灾难 ■ 埃及消息人士：停火/人质谈判将于周日恢复，援助事件推动谈判代表加快工作 ■ 也门胡塞武装击沉英国拥有的 Rubymar ■ 战争开始 148 天后您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 18:11:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-148/0000018e-0053-da4e-adbf-82fb64910000</guid></item><item><title>经过四天的游行后，数千名以色列人在耶路撒冷集会呼吁释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article/thousands-of-israelis-reach-jerusalem-after-four-day-march-calling-for-release-of-hostages/0000018e-0029-def2-a98e-cc3b44770000</link><description>随着交换协议谈判即将恢复，数千名游行者四天前从 10 月 7 日新星节大屠杀现场出发抵达耶路撒冷，要求立即释放仍被扣押在加沙地带的 134 名人质</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 17:51:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article/thousands-of-israelis-reach-jerusalem-after-four-day-march-calling-for-release-of-hostages/0000018e-0029-def2-a98e-cc3b44770000</guid></item><item><title>美国与约旦联合行动首次向加沙空投援助物资</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article/u-s-makes-its-first-gaza-aid-air-drop-in-joint-operation-with-jordan/0000018d-ffc7-da4e-adbf-ffff50df0000</link><description>美国飞机向加沙城运送了超过 38,000 份餐食。人权和国际援助组织批评美国放弃援助只是一种折衷措施，旨在掩盖美国未能进一步推动以色列允许向加沙提供必要数量的援助的事实</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 16:08:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article/u-s-makes-its-first-gaza-aid-air-drop-in-joint-operation-with-jordan/0000018d-ffc7-da4e-adbf-ffff50df0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列声称对在黎巴嫩杀害三名与伊朗有联系的真主党成员负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article/israel-claims-responsibility-for-killing-three-iran-linked-hezbollah-members-in-lebanon/0000018d-ff80-da4e-adbf-ffb9ba4e0000</link><description>以色列军队表示，它“在黎巴嫩南部袭击了一辆汽车，车上有一些向以色列领土发射火箭的恐怖分子。”据称，这些武装分子在隶属于伊朗的真主党伊玛目侯赛因分部的领导下开展活动</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 14:23:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article/israel-claims-responsibility-for-killing-three-iran-linked-hezbollah-members-in-lebanon/0000018d-ff80-da4e-adbf-ffb9ba4e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了在加沙爆炸中丧生的三名士兵的姓名； 14人受伤，其中5人伤势严重</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article-live/u-s-to-air-drop-aid-into-gaza-biden-hopeful-for-ramadan-cease-fire/0000018d-fd22-d1c2-af9f-fda7a13a0000</link><description>以色列国防军公布加沙战斗中 3 名士兵死亡、14 人受伤的信息 ■ 美国官员表示，以色列接受停火协议，执行情况取决于哈马斯释放人质 ■ 美​​国与约旦空军合作向加沙空投援助物资 ■ 加沙停火谈判埃及消息人士称，周日将在开罗恢复；据报道，以色列在派遣代表团之前等待哈马斯的回应</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 03:15:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article-live/u-s-to-air-drop-aid-into-gaza-biden-hopeful-for-ramadan-cease-fire/0000018d-fd22-d1c2-af9f-fda7a13a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军用吉普车撞倒两名巴勒斯坦青少年。然后其中一个被近距离射击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-03-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-army-jeep-hits-two-palestinian-teens-then-one-of-them-is-shot-point-blank/0000018d-fcc8-d976-a19d-fecfd76c0000</link><description>一辆以色列军用吉普车紧追两名骑电动自行车的巴勒斯坦青少年，将他们撞倒在地。一名士兵将步枪放在其中一人的脖子上并扣动扳机。 17 岁的伊姆鲁·斯维丹 (Imru Swidan) 仍处于危急状态并处于瘫痪状态</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 02:11:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-03-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-army-jeep-hits-two-palestinian-teens-then-one-of-them-is-shot-point-blank/0000018d-fcc8-d976-a19d-fecfd76c0000</guid></item><item><title>“送 300 万美元，否则我就揭露你”：一名商人、一名电影制片人和一项涉嫌以色列间谍软件的交易出了差错</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/send-3-million-or-ill-expose-you-israeli-spyware-deal-gone-awry-or-just-blackmail/0000018d-fc54-d73a-a9ed-fefd8f400000</link><description>一份向国防部提交的匿名投诉称，以色列网络世界的资深玩家埃里克·巴农 (Eric Banoun) 和他的商业伙伴玛丽亚·普莱拉 (Maria Pulera) 试图向埃及出售间谍软件。但他们坚称，一位最近出狱的前同事正试图勒索他们</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 01:36:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/send-3-million-or-ill-expose-you-israeli-spyware-deal-gone-awry-or-just-blackmail/0000018d-fc54-d73a-a9ed-fefd8f400000</guid></item><item><title>弥赛亚激进分子如何控制以色列和内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-messianic-radicals-came-to-control-israel-and-netanyahu/0000018d-fb9e-d73a-a9ed-ffbf2a610000</link><description>政治学家盖伊尔·塔尔希尔分析了弥赛亚右翼如何塑造以色列的政治领导力和格局。现在，她说，左派必须尝试做同样的事情</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 23:22:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-messianic-radicals-came-to-control-israel-and-netanyahu/0000018d-fb9e-d73a-a9ed-ffbf2a610000</guid></item><item><title>白宫表示，美军将在未来几天内向加沙空投援助物资</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-01/ty-article/u-s-military-to-airdrop-aid-into-gaza-in-coming-days-white-house-says/0000018d-fbb7-d1c2-af9f-ffb7e3560000</link><description>拜登政府表示，以色列已尝试空投并支持美国的计划，一天前巴勒斯坦人在排队寻求援助时死亡</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 20:57:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-01/ty-article/u-s-military-to-airdrop-aid-into-gaza-in-coming-days-white-house-says/0000018d-fbb7-d1c2-af9f-ffb7e3560000</guid></item><item><title>以色列可悲的警察部队预示着黑暗的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-pathetic-police-force-heralds-a-dark-future/0000018d-fb52-d1c2-af9f-fff7e4460000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 19:56:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-pathetic-police-force-heralds-a-dark-future/0000018d-fb52-d1c2-af9f-fff7e4460000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 147 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-147/0000018d-fafb-da4e-adbf-fafb59290000</link><description>联合国、法国呼吁对周四加沙北部的事件进行独立调查 ■ 埃及外长希望在斋月之前实现停火 ■ 哈马斯声称七名人质在以色列轰炸中丧生 ■ 伊朗革命卫队军官在据称以色列对叙利亚的袭击中丧生■ 欧盟委员会将向近东救济工程处支付 5000 万欧元 ■ 战争结束 147 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 17:18:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-147/0000018d-fafb-da4e-adbf-fafb59290000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗官方媒体称革命卫队顾问在叙利亚袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-01/ty-article/revolutionary-guards-adviser-killed-in-strike-in-syria-iranian-state-media-says/0000018d-fa4e-def2-a98d-fe7e21790000</link><description>叙利亚人权中心表示，叙利亚西部的巴尼亚斯是一座逊尼派城市，据悉该城市与亲伊朗民兵组织没有关系，这证明了“可以导致如此精确的袭击的情报水平”</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 15:38:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-01/ty-article/revolutionary-guards-adviser-killed-in-strike-in-syria-iranian-state-media-says/0000018d-fa4e-def2-a98d-fe7e21790000</guid></item><item><title>国际媒体谴责以色列在加沙袭击巴勒斯坦记者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-03-01/ty-article/.premium/international-media-condemns-israeli-attacks-on-palestinian-journalists-in-gaza/0000018d-f983-def2-a98d-fdb3274e0000</link><description>签署者包括美国广播公司、美联社、路透社、《纽约时报》、《华盛顿邮报》、《卫报》和《国土报》的高管。另外，数十名记者要求获准进入独立报道——以色列高等法院最近拒绝了这一请求</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 12:44:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-03-01/ty-article/.premium/international-media-condemns-israeli-attacks-on-palestinian-journalists-in-gaza/0000018d-f983-def2-a98d-fdb3274e0000</guid></item><item><title>随着伊朗继承权之战的开始，加沙战争巩固了其地位</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-03-01/ty-article/.premium/as-irans-succession-battle-begins-the-war-in-gaza-has-bolstered-its-status/0000018d-f90e-da4e-a18d-fdee0c920000</link><description>地区和国际舞台为德黑兰提供了改善其经济和国际地位的机会。然而，周五的选举为哈梅内伊执政后的第二天奠定了基础，因为伊朗面临着强大的宗教机构和革命卫队之间的选择</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 09:52:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-03-01/ty-article/.premium/as-irans-succession-battle-begins-the-war-in-gaza-has-bolstered-its-status/0000018d-f90e-da4e-a18d-fdee0c920000</guid></item></channel></rss>